To determine the type of the child object returned by the `FindParent` method in your `TextBox_Loaded` event handler, you can make use of the `GetType` method and check if the type matches each of the child types that you are interested in. Here is an example implementation:

```
private void TextBox_Loaded(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)
{
    TextBox textBox = sender as TextBox;
    object dataGrid = Utils.FindParent<object>(textBox);

    if (dataGrid != null)
    {
        Type dataType = dataGrid.GetType();

        if (dataType == typeof(ChildA))
        {
            ChildA childA = dataGrid as ChildA;
            // process childA
        }
        else if (dataType == typeof(ChildB))
        {
            ChildB childB = dataGrid as ChildB;
            // process childB
        }
        else if (dataType == typeof(ChildC))
        {
            ChildC childC = dataGrid as ChildC;
            // process childC
        }
        // ... add other child types as needed
    }
}
```

In the modified `TextBox_Loaded` event handler, we first retrieve the parent object using the `FindParent` method and store it in the `dataGrid` variable. We then check if `dataGrid` is not `null` and if it is not, determine the type of the object using the `GetType` method. We then use a series of `if` statements to check if the type is one of the child types we are interested in. If the type is a match, we cast the object to the appropriate type and process it as needed. 

Using this approach, you can handle any valid child type returned by the `FindParent` method in a flexible and extensible way.

如果元素是对象，则需要重写对象的`equals()`方法，以确保`contains()`方法的正确性。例如，如果我们有一个`Person`类，就需要重写`equals()`方法来比较两个`Person`对象的属性是否相等。然后在判断list是否包含某个`Person`对象时，就需要使用重写后的`equals()`方法。示例代码如下：

```java
List<Person> personList = new ArrayList<>();
Person p = new Person("John", "Doe");
if (!personList.contains(p)) {
    personList.add(p);
}
```

上面的代码中，我们先创建了一个`Person`对象p，并判断了personList中是否包含p，如果不包含，则将p添加到list中。

注意：在重写`equals()`方法时，通常也需要同时重写`hashCode()`方法，以确保在使用`contains()`和其它一些关于对象相等性的方法时，能够得到正确的结果。

